        <div class="single-testimonial">
            <p class="testimonial-message">
                We had struggled to find candidates who fit both our cultural and technical needs. Cobalt brought
                clarity and structure to the process. They filtered out the noise and only introduced people who were
                the right fit. They were quick, responsive, professional, and an absolute pleasure to work with.
            </p>
